data.eml:eml: Corallimorpharians (Anthozoa: Corallimorpharia) from the Argentinean Sea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Lauretta, Daniel, Martinez, Mariano I. (2019): Corallimorpharians (Anthozoa: Corallimorpharia) from the Argentinean Sea. Zootaxa 4688 (2): 249-263, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4688.2.5
